@node "hist" "History"
@next "knownbugs"
@prev "discl"
   History
   -------

V1.3 - bugs removed which made the ARexx functions unuseable. They led to heavy
       system crashes. The ARexx functions works now error free.
V1.2 - bug removed which let menucall "Remove entry" only remove _one_ entry,
       now there will be removed _all_ selected entries
     - bug removed which did let remove all selected entries at one time,
       now it does it correctly
     - replaced double image preview by a single image preview, because of
       usage of the Icon.mcc
     - some corrections at the catalog files

V1.1 - some internal code optimisations
V1.0 - some internal, but externally not noticable bugs removed
@endnode

